   DEBUG: 2026-04-20 16:40:36,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-20 16:40:36,609:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Accruals záporné → OCF > net income (typické kvůli odpisům).
   DEBUG: 2026-04-20 16:40:36,612:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 2. Korelační matice (Table 5)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-20 16:40:36,612:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Klíčové poznatky:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-20 16:40:36,612:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-20 16:40:36,612:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Volatilita vs. zpožděná vol: r = 0.61
